---
title: "US18b — Basic AI fitness plan suggestion"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>OnboardingFlow / TrainScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>GeneratePlan
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>FitnessPlan · PlannedWorkout
  A->>B: tap Generate my plan
  B->>C: generate()
  C->>E: fetchActiveGoal(userId) + fetchFitnessProfile(userId)
  E-->>C: FitnessGoal + FitnessProfile
  alt AI available
    C->>E: suggestPlan() (basic depth)
    E-->>C: plan draft (generation_strategy = basic)
  else AI unavailable
    C->>E: buildPlanSkeleton(...) rule fallback
    E-->>C: skeleton draft
  end
  C->>E: insertPlan(...) + setActivePlan(...)
  E-->>C: FitnessPlan (active)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (plan active)
  B-->>A: weekly plan, labelled AI-assisted (basic)
  note over E: suggestPlan via AiGateway → suggest-plan Edge Function (OpenAI gpt-4o-mini LIVE, Gemini/stub fallback) -<br/>Free = basic depth, Premium = personalised (US37) - goal/profile via FitnessGateway - persisted via PlanGateway
